    <briefdescription>
<para>Header file supporting ex_op for Microchip flash-controller G3 driver. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This header provides definitions for additional flash memory operations specific to the Microchip NVMCTRL G3 flash controller. It extends the standard flash driver capabilities by enabling advanced operations such as and region locking/unlocking, clear page buffer, etc.,</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This file should only be included when targeting devices with the NVMCTRL G3 flash controller. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
